This article needs to be updated. In particular: Information on currently operating networks should be updated. Note that, this article does not aim to collect all CDMA2000 (3G) networks from around the world, but intends to focus on notable deployments (WP:NOTE). cdmaOne (CDMA) (IS-95x) are not listed here. Please update this article to reflect recent events or newly available information. (December 2017)
